text: Cashmere High School is a public high school located in Cashmere, Washington. ==Athletics== ===Teams=== Cashmere's athletic teams are nicknamed The Bulldogs and Cashmere teams compete in the following sports:https://www.cashmere.wednet.edu/domain/158 *Cross Country *Football *Volleyball *Girl's Soccer *Boy's Soccer *Girl's Swimming *Boy's Swimming *Girl's Basketball *Boy's Basketball *Wrestling *Softball *Baseball *Tennis *Track and Field ==Demographics== 63% of the student population at Cashmere identify as Caucasian, 33% identify as Hispanic, 2% identify as multiracial, 1% identify as African American, 1% identify as Asian, and 1% identify as American Indian or Alaskan Native. The student body makeup is 49% male and 51% female. https://www.usnews.com/education/best-high- schools/washington/districts/cashmere-school-district/cashmere-high- school-20768/student-body ==References== Category:Public high schools in Washington (state) Category:Schools in Chelan County, Washington
